	      	<li><h5>Win a Prized game to earn the prize</h5></li>
	      	<li><h5>Play a non-Prized game and increase your future chances (like nasus stacks)</h5></li>
	    </ul>
	</div>

	<div class="col-md-6">
		<ul class="teaser-context">
	      	<h4 class="text-center"><strong>Getting started is easy</strong></h4>
		        <li><h5>Add Summoner Name -> Choose Prize Zone -> Press 'Prize Me' -> Play</h5></li>
